OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine and
OL,6,Fbright evening at first, but then
OL,7,Fturning cloudy and murky with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain and drizzle
OL,9,Fdeveloping towards midnight. Rain
OL,10,Fcontinuing overnight and turning
OL,11,Frather windy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FRain clearing the south
OL,14,Fearly in the morning to leave a sunny
OL,15,Fday for most. Winds falling light as
OL,16,Fthe day progresses so a pleasant
OL,17,Fafternoon to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
